  "title": "Changing Patterns of Tobacco and Alcohol Co-Use by Gender in the United States, 1976-2010",
  "abstract": "We conclude that co-users of tobacco and alcohol are an increasingly select subpopulation. This suggests that continued decreases in the contribution of substance use to population health and mortality may not continue apace.",
